data.description: Introducing your ideal family home! This unique and well maintained 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath beauty is a true gem in a fantastic neighborhood. While outside you'll notice the new Hardie-Board siding, New vinyl windows and the large 8,000 sq.ft. lot that provides plenty of parking for your vehicles, RV, Boat and toys. Once you step onto the covered front porch, you'll immediately appreciate the well-manicured front lawn and the home's striking curb appeal. Upon entering, the living room is equally impressive providing vaulted ceilings, an open concept layout and an abundance of natural light that floods every corner, making this space feel warm and welcoming. From the living area, you have easy access to the kitchen, where you will find an eatery bar, ample cupboard and counter space, a built-in dishwasher and matching appliances. Located right off the kitchen, conveniently built is the attached oversized garage, making grocery trips a breeze. The main level of the home is also equipped with a cozy fireplace that provides a perfect focal point for gatherings and relaxation as well as a half bath for ultimate convenience. Heading upstairs you will enter into the Primary suite, which is complete with an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in shower. Also, on the upper level you will find another full bathroom as well as two additional bedrooms that offer tons of space for your family, guests or a dedicated home office. Step outside to your own private oasis, featuring an extensive deck perfect for entertaining and a large, fenced backyard that's exceptional for kids and pets. This unique charmer offers a peaceful and friendly community with schools, parks and amenities nearby. Enjoy the convenience of shopping, dining, and entertainment just moments away, all while living in a tranquil and safe environment. Don't miss this opportunity to make this stunning property your forever home. Schedule a showing today.
